highlights.text: “FELLINI (feat. Kid Yugi)” by Ernia and Kid Yugi is the highest new entry on Top Songs Italy at #1.
“Destri” by Gazzelle has been on Top Songs Italy the longest, at 999 days straight.
Sfera Ebbasta has the most spots on Top Songs Italy. “Yakuza” is the highest at #20.
“AMICI COME PRIMA” by 333 Mob, Lazza, and Low Kidd is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Italy, up 62 spots at #51.
